{{zh-hanzi|[[首]][[屈]][[一]][[指]]}}
==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: shŏu qū yì zhĭ
===Etymology===
Literally: the first bent finger
*In Chinese culture, one common method of counting is to begin with an open hand, then begin folding the fingers into the palm starting with the thumb.

===Idiom===
# [[first]]
#: ''[[開通]][[網路]][[共享]][[救助]][[訊息]]，[[這]][[一]][[做法]][[不僅]][[在]][[成都]][[尚]][[屬]][[首次]]，[[在]][[全國]][[也]][[是]]'''首屈一指'''。 ''
#: ''[[开通]][[网络]][[共享]][[救助]][[信息]]，[[这]][[一]][[做法]][[不仅]][[在]][[成都]][[尚]][[属]][[首次]]，[[在]][[全国]][[也]][[是]]'''首屈一指'''。''[http://72.14.235.104/search?q=cache:aMeWakRCausJ:www.chinainfo.gov.cn/data/200607/1_20060704_140362.html+%22%E9%A6%96%E5%B1%88%E4%B8%80%E6%8C%87%22+site:.cn&hl=zh-CN&gl=cn&ct=clnk&cd=10]
#: ''Not only is this a first for Chengdu in terms of sharing help information over the net, it is the [[first]] in the country''.
# number one; come first on the list; be matchless; be second to none; come out first; endsville; thumbs up.
#: ''[[苗族]][[的]][[銀]][[飾]][[在]][[各]][[民族]][[的]][[首飾]][[中]]'''首屈一指'''''
#: ''[[苗族]][[的]][[银]][[饰]][[在]][[各]][[民族]][[的]][[首饰]][[中]]'''首屈一指'''''[http://72.14.235.104/search?q=cache:UjxP3kNs4rUJ:www.ccnt.com.cn/nation/index2.htm%3Fdir%3Dfc%257Cduds%26id%3D20010412043+%22%E9%A6%96%E5%B1%88%E4%B8%80%E6%8C%87%22+site:.cn&hl=zh-CN&gl=cn&ct=clnk&cd=1]
#: ''The silver jewelry of the [[w:Hmong people|Hmong people]] comes in '''first''' place out of all of ethnic jewelry.''

